snippet.title: Judge LOSES IT After Amber Heard Begs For The Case To Get Thrown Out AGAIN...
snippet.description:
At this point in time, you honestly have to wonder if we're ever going to be rid of this case between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. Mainly because the two are seemingly intertwined with a great many things and every time one of them seems to have a victory in hand, the other pulls out the rug from them and suddenly they have the advantage. Recently, Amber Heard has been doing everything in her power to try and get the defamation case against Johnny Depp thrown out, but it hasn't been working, and the case will definitely be going to court now. We'll break it down for you Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the situation with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp and why their court case will indeed be going to court despite what Head has done. Do you think that Amber is downright desperate at this point to try and get rid of this case? Do you think that Johnny will be able to work this in his favor as we get even closer to the court date? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
